{"id": "QmdgAH88QnayNB3QzdP8mEcupxN8Lpr3wHFzCCCz3LQt3o", "title": "[BIP-16] - New BAS Emissions Schedule", "body": "### **[BIP-16] - New BAS Emissions Schedule (Amendment and Implementation of BIP-13)**\nAuthors: @qa1q, @yyctrader\n\nAs BIP-13 passed nearly 2 months ago, the proposed BAS emissions schedule has been updated and adjusted accordingly and is now ready to be implemented on 5/31/2021.\n\n### Currently, the protocol is emitting 18,643 BASv2/week\n\n### The emissions schedule will be modified as below:\nWeek 27 (5/31) \u2013 Reduction to 15,182 BASv2 (approx. 18%)\nWeek 28 onwards \u2013 11% reductions\n\n### The previously proposed annual inflation will also be amended:\nYear 2 \u2013 4% (previously 5%)\nYear 3 \u2013 3.5% (previously 4%)\nYear 4 \u2013 3% (no change)\nYear 5 and beyond \u2013 2% (no change)\n\nWe believe that the modified schedule will allow us to maintain the intent of BIP-13 despite the delayed implementation, as we will reach 1M BAS minted in Week 333 (7 years) and ensure that we have ongoing emissions to incentivize protocol growth while maintaining scarcity.\n\nThe complete emissions schedule can be seen here:\nhttps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1yE_tPvadT_oLRvHUAqEks19bwLBq3yMeE4PacBC_BQM", "choices": ["Implement BIP-16 on 5/31", "Do Nothing"], "start": 1622008740, "end": 1622095140, "snapshot": "12507997", "state": "closed", "author": "0x0819915F548E3b635af0d715a46eBc982650550c", "space": {"id": "basiscash.eth", "name": "BasisCash"}, "votes": 34, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmbMNt5CfU2ifoEV5DzarL6Ry2sMjouqVbwxTVyyjkNwuT", "voter": "0x424687a2BB8B34F93c3DcB5E3Cdd2AD6A21163Bf", "created": 1622061390, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "basiscash.eth"}}, {"id": "QmTy6tcXhWKd8JopPPWd6Ut4TNdmbkPVS7PZbpYJSXtcnC", "voter": "0x5136ceC13DaA3ef59B34bF4e5317556CC1c4C549", "created": 1622060485, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "basiscash.eth"}}, {"id": "QmRMnmsmhefPYNbZmuFYJUWFHVi9WGzDfieSfRtr39SCdz", "voter": "0x89808C49F858b86E80B892506CF11606Fb25fCDC